ActAgricultural Products Marketing Act
SubjectSaskatchewan Winter Cereals Order
PrecisSASKATCHEWAN WINTER CEREALS ORDER to (1) strengthen and expand the commodity boards’ authority that will regulate the interprovincial and export trade of their commodity; and (2) allow for the collection of levies in interprovincial and export trade to the same extent as those collected for intraprovincial trade.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2013-0242 Publication Date: 2014-01-01
